5
00:00:53,500 --> 00:00:53,860
Suqing.

6
00:00:54,260 --> 00:00:54,780
You must be tired.

7
00:00:55,540 --> 00:00:56,340
You should go home.

8
00:00:56,340 --> 00:00:57,300
