110
00:06:20,460 --> 00:06:21,620
is meaningless?

111
00:06:22,860 --> 00:06:23,340
Things have come to this,

112
00:06:23,340 --> 00:06:24,500
I have nothing else to say.

113
00:06:27,500 --> 00:06:28,580
I used you.

114
00:06:31,820 --> 00:06:32,900
If you can't get over it,

115
00:06:35,700 --> 00:06:36,740
let's get a divorce.

116
00:06:39,300 --> 00:06:40,500
But I will stay in Jueshi Group

117
00:06:42,020 --> 00:06:43,140
