118
00:06:45,780 --> 00:06:46,700
I will move out tomorrow.

119
00:06:49,500 --> 00:06:50,060
This...

120
00:06:52,020 --> 00:06:52,740
You can have it back.

121
00:07:00,700 --> 00:07:02,180
(Why don't you understand?)

122
00:07:03,660 --> 00:07:05,260
