to save Mo Zhenfeng too, right?)

127
00:07:24,460 --> 00:07:26,100
You're one of the best lawyers
in the city.

128
00:07:26,300 --> 00:07:27,860
Even you don't have confidence
in this lawsuit?

129
00:07:28,300 --> 00:07:29,020
